<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 27 Jun 2026 02:00:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>迈克尔·塞勒 (Michael Saylor) 在新应变中的策略是关键阈值突破</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-26/bitcoin-s-biggest-corporate-buyer-reels-as-funding-edge-vanishes</link><description>迈克尔·塞勒 (Michael Saylor) 伟大的加密实验很快就失去了信徒。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWjRWNybhPB4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 17:32:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-26/bitcoin-s-biggest-corporate-buyer-reels-as-funding-edge-vanishes</guid></item><item><title>加密货币的 ETF 繁荣在残酷的一周中得到了 45 亿美元的现实检验</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-26/crypto-s-etf-boom-gets-4-5-billion-reality-check-in-brutal-week</link><description>原本应该为比特币带来稳定的投资者正在退出。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3AhbNNWsLS8/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 16:47:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-26/crypto-s-etf-boom-gets-4-5-billion-reality-check-in-brutal-week</guid></item><item><title>随着加密货币下滑，Cantor Bitcoin SPAC 让投资者减少认捐</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-26/cantor-bitcoin-spac-lets-investors-commit-less-as-crypto-slides</link><description>与 Cantor Fitzgerald 相关的一家空白支票公司正试图通过允许投资者投入比最初承诺更少的资金来支持即将到来的加密货币交易。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.ydzP4whAlA/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 14:01:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-26/cantor-bitcoin-spac-lets-investors-commit-less-as-crypto-slides</guid></item><item><title>比特币探底者担心 1.3 万亿美元暴跌后会带来新的痛苦</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-26/bitcoin-bottom-hunters-fear-fresh-pain-after-1-3-trillion-rout</link><description>比特币的崩溃迫使加密货币资深人士面对每个熊市最终都会提出的问题：大规模恐慌何时会创造买入机会？许多经历过以往繁荣与萧条周期的投资者和分析师认为，答案是：还没有。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQYxqHsBiVSo/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 12:05:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-26/bitcoin-bottom-hunters-fear-fresh-pain-after-1-3-trillion-rout</guid></item><item><title>随着人工智能电力需求飙升，陷入困境的比特币矿工的一个亮点</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-25/bitcoin-btc-miners-help-electric-grid-as-ai-data-centers-boom</link><description>矿工可以为电网带来好处。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.V9vyUYcOXY/v22/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-25/bitcoin-btc-miners-help-electric-grid-as-ai-data-centers-boom</guid></item><item><title>迈克尔·塞勒失败的融资模式震惊了比特币交易者</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-25/michael-saylor-s-misfiring-funding-model-jolts-bitcoin-traders</link><description>对迈克尔·塞勒(Michael Saylor)的比特币购买机器开始失灵的担忧正在席卷整个加密货币市场，加剧了比特币的最新一轮抛售，并暴露了过去两年支撑全球最大加密货币需求的金融结构之一的裂缝。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i7p5zlwaJy68/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 17:13:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-25/michael-saylor-s-misfiring-funding-model-jolts-bitcoin-traders</guid></item><item><title>比特币价值 100 亿美元的期权到期风险加剧抛售</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-25/bitcoin-s-woes-could-be-compounded-by-10-billion-options-expiry</link><description>比特币正面临大规模期权到期，这可能会给已经在机构需求减弱和宏观经济逆风中苦苦挣扎的市场带来更大压力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i14rCG_hn7z4/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 04:39:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-25/bitcoin-s-woes-could-be-compounded-by-10-billion-options-expiry</guid></item></channel></rss>